high_descs: Go to the shelf behind you.
Take the cup from the second shelf.
Bring the cup to the fridge.
Chill the cup in the fridge.
Go to the coffee maker on the counter to the left of the sink.
Put the cup in the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled cup in the coffee maker.

high_descs: Turn around and head left to the shelving structure to the left.
Pick up the mug on the second to bottom shelf.
Turn right and go forward a couple steps, then turn left and face the fridge.
Place the mug in the fridge and close the door. Wait a moment, then take out the mug.
Turn right and hang right to walk to the coffee maker.
Place the mug in the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled mug in a coffee maker.

high_descs: turn to the right, go to the shelf in the room, and turn to face it
pick up the mug on the middle shelf
turn right and head to the refrigerator across the room
open the refrigerator, place the mug on the shelf with the tomato, close the refrigerator, wait 7 seconds, open the refrigerator, take the mug
turn around and take the mug to the coffee maker next to the sink
place the mug on the metal shelf of the coffee maker
anns.task_desc: Place a cool mug into the coffee maker
